<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Zero Hunger Project</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the Zero Hunger Project, an initiative dedicated to ending hunger, achieving food security, improving nutrition, and promoting sustainable agriculture.</p>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About the Project</h2>
        <p>The Zero Hunger Project aligns with the United Nations' Sustainable Development Goal 2: Zero Hunger. Our mission is to connect surplus food from restaurants and caterers with those in need, ensuring that everyone has access to nutritious meals.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>We believe that a world without hunger is possible if we work together and make the most of our abundant resources. Our mission is to reduce food waste and distribute surplus food to underserved communities across the city.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="get-involved">
        <h2>Get Involved</h2>
        <p>
            Join us in our efforts to make a difference. Whether you are a restaurant owner looking to donate food, a volunteer willing to contribute your time, or a donor who wants to support our cause financially, there's a role for everyone in the Zero Hunger Project.
        </p>
    </section>

</div>
